import React from "react"; import { Box, Grid, Paper, Card, CardActionArea, CardContent, Typography, CardMedia, } from "@mui/material"; import { experimentalStyled as styled } from "@mui/material/styles"; export default function DashboardCards() { const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({ backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === "dark" ? "#1A2027" : "#fff", ...theme.typography.body2, padding: theme.spacing(2), textAlign: "center", color: theme.palette.text.secondary, })); return (
{Array.from(Array(4)).map((_, index) => ( Lizard Lizards are a widespread group of squamate reptiles, with over 6,000 species, ranging across all continents except Antarctica ))}
); }
